Remeber to install the libftd2xx code:

From ~/foreign/libftd2xx/release/build:

	mkdir -p /usr/local/ftd2xx/{lib,include}
	cp libftd2xx.a libftd2xx.so.1.4.22 /usr/local/ftd2xx/lib/
	chmod 0755 /usr/local/ftd2xx/lib/libftd2xx.so.1.4.22
	ln -sf /usr/local/ftd2xx/lib/libftd2xx.so.1.4.22 /usr/local/ftd2xx/lib/libftd2xx.so
	cp ../*.h /usr/local/ftd2xx/include

NOTE! Access to FT232H (without device driver) may require root priviledges!
